channel.title: Juice
channel.desc: Guy doesn't want to see Jamma anymore, so when Jamma meets a magical stranger who offers to unburden him from his clownish ways to win Guy back, he decides to take the deal and is transformed. Guy has a photoshoot for his book cover, but he doesn't want to look boring, so Isaac offers to style him in exchange for free therapy.
